Traditional control methods what existed operability and real-time issues; We proposed a solution based on Web Service technology to achieve remote control system, and PLC as the control object, we established feasible communication between PC and lower computer; Combined with JAVA language develop WEB page as the control system of the client and write serial communication, as well as published it online and remote controlled it by INTERNET system; Experiment shows that the remote control system improve the controllability of the equipment and condition monitoring in real time, which has a high significance and practical value.